title: Number of suppliers to take to further competition

form.question1: Enter a number for the amount of suppliers you would like to take to further competition.
form.question2: All the suppliers you choose to take forward, who also apply for your opportunity, will need to be evaluated. For example, if you choose to take forward 50 suppliers, and all suppliers apply, you will need to evaluate 50 suppliers.
